---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const pageTitle = "Sobre Mí - Pedro Carranza | Software Strategist";
const pageDescription = "Conoce la mente detrás de la estrategia. Más de una década transformando sistemas legacy en arquitecturas modernas.";
---

<Layout title={pageTitle} description={pageDescription}>

<section class="min-h-screen bg-[#0e3146] text-white relative overflow-hidden py-24">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.03] pointer-events-none" 
       style="background-image: radial-gradient(#2a99c9 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 30px 30px;">
  </div>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      
      <div class="text-center mb-20">
        <span class="font-['Orbitron'] text-[#2a99c9] text-[10px] tracking-[0.5em] uppercase mb-4 block">System_Core / Bio</span>
        <h1 class="font-['Orbitron'] text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold mb-6 tracking-tight text-white uppercase">
          SOBRE <span class="text-[#2a99c9]">MÍ</span>
        </h1>
        <div class="w-32 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#2a99c9] to-[#e9691e] mx-auto rounded-full"></div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-16 items-start">
        
        <div class="lg:col-span-5 lg:sticky lg:top-24">
          <div class="relative group">
            <div class="absolute -inset-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#2a99c9] to-[#e9691e] rounded-2xl blur opacity-20 group-hover:opacity-40 transition duration-1000"></div>
            
            <div class="relative w-full aspect-square bg-[#0a1e2b] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-white/10 shadow-2xl">
              <img
                src="/images/pedro-profile.png" 
                alt="Pedro Carranza"
                class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700"
              />
              <div class="absolute top-4 left-4 opacity-40">
                <img src="/pc-monogram-white.svg" alt="" class="w-12 h-12" />
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 mt-8">
            <div class="p-4 bg-white/5 rounded-xl border border-white/5">
              <div class="text-[#2a99c9] font-['Orbitron'] text-2xl font-bold">+10</div>
              <div class="text-[9px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest mt-1">Años de Exp.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-4 bg-white/5 rounded-xl border border-white/5">
              <div class="text-[#e9691e] font-['Orbitron'] text-2xl font-bold">Muchos</div>
              <div class="text-[9px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest mt-1">Estudiantes</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="lg:col-span-7 space-y-12">
          
          <section>
            <h2 class="font-['Orbitron'] text-sm font-bold mb-6 text-[#2a99c9] tracking-[0.3em] uppercase">
              La Mente Detrás de la Estrategia
            </h2>
            <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl leading-snug text-white font-light italic border-l-4 border-[#e9691e] pl-8 py-2">
              "No creo en la tecnología por la tecnología misma, sino como el motor que escala un negocio."
            </p>
          </section>
          
          <div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-slate-300 font-['Inter'] leading-relaxed">
            <div class="mt-4 flex items-center gap-2 text-[10px] font-['Fira+Code'] text-slate-500 uppercase">
              <span class="relative flex h-2 w-2">
                <span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-green-400 opacity-75"></span>
                <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-green-500"></span>
              </span>
              SUCRE_BO: {new Date().toLocaleTimeString('es-BO', { hour: '2-digit', minute: '2-digit', timeZone: 'America/La_Paz' })} AST
            </div>
            <p>
              Desde Sucre, Bolivia, he navegado todas las capas del desarrollo de software. Mi carrera no se limita a escribir código; se trata de <strong>diseñar arquitecturas que sobrevivan al tiempo</strong>.
            </p>
            <p>
              He liderado proyectos críticos en sectores de pagos y sistemas transaccionales, donde la precisión no es opcional. Esa misma rigurosidad es la que llevo a la academia como docente universitario, formando a quienes construirán el futuro digital.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="grid gap-6">
            <div class="bg-white/[0.03] p-6 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 hover:bg-white/[0.05] transition-all group">
              <h4 class="text-[10px] font-['Orbitron'] text-[#2a99c9] mb-3 tracking-[0.4em] uppercase">Evolución de Sistemas</h4>
              <p class="text-white font-bold mb-2">Modernización de Cero a Uno</p>
              <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">Transformo el código legacy en APIs modernas y escalables sin interrumpir tu flujo de caja.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white/[0.03] p-6 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 hover:bg-white/[0.05] transition-all group">
              <h4 class="text-[10px] font-['Orbitron'] text-[#e9691e] mb-3 tracking-[0.4em] uppercase">De Bits a Bots</h4>
              <p class="text-white font-bold mb-2">IA con Propósito Estratégico</p>
              <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">Integro modelos de lenguaje y automatización para resolver ineficiencias operativas reales.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section class="py-24 bg-[#0a1e2b] border-t border-white/5">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
    
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center mb-16 gap-4">
      <h3 class="font-['Orbitron'] text-2xl text-white uppercase tracking-widest">
        Technical <span class="text-[#2a99c9]">Stack</span>
      </h3>
      <div class="h-px flex-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#2a99c9]/50 to-transparent mx-8 hidden md:block"></div>
      <span class="text-slate-500 font-['Fira+Code'] text-xs">v2.0.25 // Stable</span>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-[#e9691e] rounded-full animate-pulse"></div>
          <h4 class="font-['Orbitron'] text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Intelligence Layer</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          {['Python', 'LangChain', 'OpenAI SDK', 'RAG Architecture', 'Pandas', 'NLP'].map(skill => (
            <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-[#e9691e]/10 border border-[#e9691e]/30 text-[#e9691e] font-['Fira+Code'] text-[10px] rounded-md">
              {skill}
            </span>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-[#2a99c9] rounded-full"></div>
          <h4 class="font-['Orbitron'] text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Logic Layer</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          {['Node.js', 'Go', 'PHP (Legacy)', 'Microservices', 'REST APIs', 'PostgreSQL'].map(skill => (
            <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-[#2a99c9]/10 border border-[#2a99c9]/30 text-[#2a99c9] font-['Fira+Code'] text-[10px] rounded-md">
              {skill}
            </span>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-white/40 rounded-full"></div>
          <h4 class="font-['Orbitron'] text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Infra Layer</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          {['Docker', 'CI/CD', 'AWS', 'Linux Server', 'Git', 'Clean Code'].map(skill => (
            <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-white/5 border border-white/20 text-white/70 font-['Fira+Code'] text-[10px] rounded-md">
              {skill}
            </span>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="mt-20 pt-10 border-t border-white/5 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-8">
    <div>
      <h4 class="font-['Orbitron'] text-white text-lg mb-2 text-center md:text-left">¿Listo para la evolución digital?</h4>
      <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm font-['Inter']">Hablemos sobre cómo transformar tus bits en bots inteligentes.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 w-full md:w-auto">
      <a href="/contacto" class="px-8 py-4 bg-[#e9691e] text-white font-['Orbitron'] text-[10px] font-bold tracking-[0.2em] rounded-xl hover:bg-[#d8581a] transition-all text-center shadow-lg shadow-[#e9691e]/20">
        INICIAR PROYECTO
      </a>
      
      <a href="/files/CV-Pedro-Carranza.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" download="CV-Pedro-Carranza.pdf" class="px-8 py-4 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-white font-['Orbitron'] text-[10px] font-bold tracking-[0.2em] rounded-xl hover:bg-white/10 transition-all flex items-center justify-center gap-3">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-4 h-4 text-[#2a99c9]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 10v6m0 0l-3-3m3 3l3-3m2 8H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
        </svg>
        DOWNLOAD_CV.PDF
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
  </div>
</section>

</Layout>
